# Ingress
## Installation
helm upgrade --install ingress-nginx ingress-nginx \
  --repo https://kubernetes.github.io/ingress-nginx \
  --namespace reverse-proxy --create-namespace

kubectl get service --namespace reverse-proxy ingress-nginx-controller --output wide --watch
https://onairotich.medium.com/services-and-ingress-7afc517f2ec6
https://kubernetes.io/docs/concepts/services-networking/ingress/#tls

